@page "/components"

<PageTitle>开源组件-九零工坊</PageTitle>

<MudGrid>
    <MudItem xs="12" Class="mt-6">
        <MudCard Elevation="8" Class="pa-4" Style="background-color: white;">
            <MudText Typo="Typo.h5" Color="Color.Primary" Class="mb-4">开源组件</MudText>
            <MudGrid Spacing="4" Class="mt-4">
                <MudItem xs="12">
                    <MudCard Style="background-color: white;">
                        <MudCardHeader>
                            <CardHeaderAvatar>
                                <MudAvatar Size="Size.Large">
                                    <MudImage Src="/images/component/auto-upgrade.png" Alt="JiuLing.AutoUpgrade" />
                                </MudAvatar>
                            </CardHeaderAvatar>
                            <CardHeaderContent>
                                <MudText Typo="Typo.h6">JiuLing.AutoUpgrade</MudText>
                                <MudImage Src="https://img.shields.io/github/license/JiuLing-zhang/JiuLing.AutoUpgrade" Class="mr-2" />
                                <MudImage Src="https://img.shields.io/nuget/v/JiuLing.AutoUpgrade" Class="mr-2" />
                                <MudImage Src="https://img.shields.io/nuget/dt/JiuLing.AutoUpgrade" />
                            </CardHeaderContent>
                        </MudCardHeader>
                        <MudCardContent>
                            <MudText Typo="Typo.body2">
                                一个简单、易用的自动更新组件。快速集成，为开发者提供开箱即用的自动更新解决方案，让软件更新变得更加轻松。更新程序的核心程序是基于 .NET Framework 4.7 开发的 x64 格式的程序，所以使用此组件之前，请先确保客户端环境能够运行该程序。
                            </MudText>
                        </MudCardContent>
                        <MudCardActions>
                            <MudButton Href="https://www.nuget.org/packages/JiuLing.AutoUpgrade" Target="_blank" Variant="Variant.Text" Color="Color.Primary">NuGet</MudButton>
                            <MudButton Href="https://github.com/JiuLing-zhang/JiuLing.AutoUpgrade" Target="_blank" Variant="Variant.Text" Color="Color.Primary">GitHub</MudButton>
                        </MudCardActions>
                    </MudCard>
                </MudItem>

                <MudItem xs="12">
                    <MudCard Style="background-color: white;">
                        <MudCardHeader>
                            <CardHeaderAvatar>
                                <MudAvatar Size="Size.Large">
                                    <MudImage Src="/images/component/common-libs.png" Alt="JiuLing.CommonLibs" />
                                </MudAvatar>
                            </CardHeaderAvatar>
                            <CardHeaderContent>
                                <MudText Typo="Typo.h6">JiuLing.CommonLibs</MudText>
                                <MudImage Src="https://img.shields.io/github/license/JiuLing-zhang/JiuLing.CommonLibs" Class="mr-2" />
                                <MudImage Src="https://img.shields.io/nuget/v/JiuLing.CommonLibs" Class="mr-2" />
                                <MudImage Src="https://img.shields.io/nuget/dt/JiuLing.CommonLibs" />
                            </CardHeaderContent>
                        </MudCardHeader>
                        <MudCardContent>
                            <MudText Typo="Typo.body2">
                                一个通用类库。目前包含的功能有：Dictionary对象对比工具、枚举描述、字符串扩展、日志、通用模型、Cookie工具、网络请求工具、操作系统版本帮助类、随机数、MD5、SHA1、正则表达式、时间戳、线程帮助类、Guid帮助类、程序版本帮助类、命令行参数解析工具。
                            </MudText>
                        </MudCardContent>
                        <MudCardActions>
                            <MudButton Href="https://www.nuget.org/packages/JiuLing.CommonLibs" Target="_blank" Variant="Variant.Text" Color="Color.Primary">NuGet</MudButton>
                            <MudButton Href="https://github.com/JiuLing-zhang/JiuLing.CommonLibs" Target="_blank" Variant="Variant.Text" Color="Color.Primary">GitHub</MudButton>
                        </MudCardActions>
                    </MudCard>
                </MudItem>

                <MudItem xs="12">
                    <MudCard Style="background-color: white;">
                        <MudCardHeader>
                            <CardHeaderAvatar>
                                <MudAvatar Size="Size.Large">
                                    <MudImage Src="/images/component/excel-export.png" Alt="JiuLing.ExcelExport" />
                                </MudAvatar>
                            </CardHeaderAvatar>
                            <CardHeaderContent>
                                <MudText Typo="Typo.h6">JiuLing.ExcelExport</MudText>
                                <MudImage Src="https://img.shields.io/github/license/JiuLing-zhang/JiuLing.ExcelExport" Class="mr-2" />
                                <MudImage Src="https://img.shields.io/nuget/v/JiuLing.ExcelExport" Class="mr-2" />
                                <MudImage Src="https://img.shields.io/nuget/dt/JiuLing.ExcelExport" />
                            </CardHeaderContent>
                        </MudCardHeader>
                        <MudCardContent>
                            <MudText Typo="Typo.body2">
                                一个基于 Excel 模板导出的组件（基于 NPOI）。轻松配置，仅仅配置模板和数据源即可一键导出，支持多 Sheet导出。
                            </MudText>
                        </MudCardContent>
                        <MudCardActions>
                            <MudButton Href="https://www.nuget.org/packages/JiuLing.ExcelExport" Target="_blank" Variant="Variant.Text" Color="Color.Primary">NuGet</MudButton>
                            <MudButton Href="https://github.com/JiuLing-zhang/JiuLing.ExcelExport" Target="_blank" Variant="Variant.Text" Color="Color.Primary">GitHub</MudButton>
                        </MudCardActions>
                    </MudCard>
                </MudItem>
            </MudGrid>
        </MudCard>
    </MudItem>
</MudGrid>